# Intersection of Two Arrays

## Description

[doc](https://leetcode.com/problems/intersection-of-two-arrays/)

## Solutions

### First Idea

```javascript
/**
 * @param {number[]} nums1
 * @param {number[]} nums2
 * @return {number[]}
 */
var intersection = function (nums1, nums2) {
  const nums2Set = new Set(nums2)
  return [...new Set(nums1)].filter((v) => nums2Set.has(v))
}
```

- Time Complexity: O(n)
- Space Complexity: O(n)
